data.description: Beautiful home in Hillside Terrace. This home has amazing features such as a huge living room with trey ceiling and a beautiful corner fireplace, granite throughout, the kitchen has under cabinet lighting and a pantry. The isolated master has his/hers closets, double vanity, and separate tub and shower. You will enjoy the evenings on the back patio. It also has radiant wrap under the brick for energy efficiency, which help with electric bill on this ALL electric home. DON'T MISS OUT ON THIS ONE!!!!
